      "content": "{\n  \"cwd\": \"/Users/sam.zhang/Documents/codex-supervisor\",\n  \"execution_layer_policy\": {\n    \"agentic_lead_policy\": {\n      \"min_subagents\": 3,\n      \"policy\": \"off\",\n      \"required_evidence_grade\": \"self_reported\",\n      \"required_roles\": [],\n      \"solo_exception_for_artifact_only_gates\": false\n    },\n    \"allowed_dynamic_workflow_task_classes\": [],\n    \"codex_supervises_final_artifact\": true,\n    \"dynamic_workflow_task_class\": null,\n    \"lead_execution_layer\": \"single_lead_worker\",\n    \"mode\": \"lead_direct\",\n    \"preview_required_gates\": [],\n    \"supervision_layer\": \"codex_plus_lead\"\n  },\n  \"expected_decisions\": [],\n  \"expected_objections\": [],\n  \"expected_specialists\": [],\n  \"gate\": \"outcome_review\",\n  \"injected_lesson_block\": \"Known failure modes to verify before claiming\\nThese are advisory lessons from previous supervisor runs. They do not satisfy any gate by themselves.\\n1. [FM-1.5] Unaware of termination conditions (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Verify this known failure mode explicitly before claiming the gate is complete.\\n2. [FM-2.4] Information withholding (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Address independent reviewer objections with concrete evidence references.\\n3. [FM-1.3] Step repetition (source_run_id=f89bc699-1b4e-4713-95b7-d1493a3acfd8): Change the plan or evidence before retrying; do not repeat the same handoff.\\n4. [FM-1.3] Step repetition (source_run_id=d84b43e3-70de-4f95-b2dc-c7f9aca8684f): Change the plan or evidence before retrying; do not repeat the same handoff.\\n5. [runtime_evidence_failed] unknown (source_run_id=d84b43e3-70de-4f95-b2dc-c7f9aca8684f): Verify this known failure mode explicitly before claiming the gate is complete.\",\n  \"injected_lesson_block_sha256\": \"0d1c472ed49da78c6304a106dac218c15724da3a82555841610b38e002676b29\",\n  \"injected_lesson_ids\": [\n    \"lesson-49755707839e187